{"tid":923501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊客驚！動物園猩猩伸手揉捏女員工奶奶","createTime":"2018-12-01T10:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T01:07:35.000Z","uid":32511,"like":658,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"66159c2987f6c41ec261fa90713cdfba64727f15","tid":923501,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:02:35.000Z","msg":"泰國曼谷野生動物園（Safari World）的猩猩，在跟遊客合照的時候，伸手偷捏女員工的胸部。<br />\n <br />\n據《太陽報》報導，動物園女員工抱著猩猩給遊客合照，此時猩猩突然伸出右手，往女員工的左胸襲去，並且揉捏了幾下開始大笑，讓26歲的女員工驚呆了。而影片中也可以聽到遊客大喊，「牠正在按摩，牠正在按摩」。另一名動物園員工表示，他覺得猩猩知道自己在幹嘛，因為這樣可以讓遊客大笑，「我們之後會告訴牠，以後不要再這樣做了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Qm0m3P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Qm0m3P.png&h=affdb06d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f8a887adb0fc63119b38150a5a2ad4f93fbfa9f","tid":923501,"uid":95541,"like":2095,"dislike":4,"score":2091,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"咁樣衰一定係猩猩中的毒撚"},{"pid":"6c9525781c82221fdf789e50d3a41febf1e8e052","tid":923501,"uid":50744,"like":1416,"dislike":7,"score":1409,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"連猩猩都有波揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8bc4212bef4ee38907c2ec06af871508b1130c","tid":923501,"uid":143499,"like":272,"dislike":7,"score":265,"quote":{"pid":"6f8a887adb0fc63119b38150a5a2ad4f93fbfa9f","tid":923501,"uid":95541,"like":2095,"dislike":4,"score":2091,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"咁樣衰一定係猩猩中的毒撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚都有得揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67c20c9086f654eb5a5c032967f864c134409b5","tid":923501,"uid":45368,"like":737,"dislike":5,"score":732,"quote":{"pid":"7e8bc4212bef4ee38907c2ec06af871508b1130c","tid":923501,"uid":143499,"like":272,"dislike":7,"score":265,"quote":{"pid":"6f8a887adb0fc63119b38150a5a2ad4f93fbfa9f","tid":923501,"uid":95541,"like":2095,"dislike":4,"score":2091,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2